title: (Wed Early Bird) We Play Country Artist or Philosopher + Abby Shares Her Hiccup Hack and a Dating Update + Being Treated Better Because Of Your Outfit?
itunes:title: (Wed Early Bird) We Play Country Artist or Philosopher + Abby Shares Her Hiccup Hack and a Dating Update + Being Treated Better Because Of Your Outfit?
description:
We play Country Artist or Philosopher! Bobby reads famous quotes, and we have to guess if a country artist or philosopher said it. Plus, Abby tells us her hack on how to get rid of hiccups and shares a dating update. Then, we discuss a study that says if you dress better at a restaurant, you'll get better service. We share if this has happened to us.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
